description:
# Add Freight Agents
Freight Agents are third-party representatives who assist in handling shipments, documentation, and coordination at origin or destination ports.

In ERPNext, Freight Agent records include company name, contact details, service areas, and role (e.g., origin agent, destination agent). They are linked to bookings to manage local clearance, delivery, and communication.
